  "content": [
    {
      "chapterUid": 148,
      "chapterTitle": "第一章 食蓼少年",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "33638775_13_1121-1132",
          "range": "43222-43233",
          "rangeStart": 43222,
          "rangeEnd": 43233,
          "markText": "故乡飘已远，往意浩无边",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1647590978,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2022-03-18 16:09:38",
          "chapterUid": 148,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=33638775&chapterUid=148&rangeStart=43222&rangeEnd=43233",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ed732f2072014977ed74bf5?chapterUid=148&rangeStart=43222&rangeEnd=43233"
        },
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "33638775_13_683-746",
          "range": "42720-42783",
          "rangeStart": 42720,
          "rangeEnd": 42783,
          "markText": "岷山之阳土如腴，江水清滑多鲤鱼。古人居之富者众，我独厌倦思移居。经行天下爱嵩岳，遂欲买地居妻孥。晴原漫漫望不尽，山色照野光如濡",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1647590910,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2022-03-18 16:08:30",
          "chapterUid": 148,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=33638775&chapterUid=148&rangeStart=42720&rangeEnd=42783",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ed732f2072014977ed74bf5?chapterUid=148&rangeStart=42720&rangeEnd=42783"
        },
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "33638775_9_1296-1306",
          "range": "17500-17510",
          "rangeStart": 17500,
          "rangeEnd": 17510,
          "markText": "冰肌玉骨，自清凉无汗",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1647392364,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2022-03-16 08:59:24",
          "chapterUid": 148,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=33638775&chapterUid=148&rangeStart=17500&rangeEnd=17510",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ed732f2072014977ed74bf5?chapterUid=148&rangeStart=17500&rangeEnd=17510"
        },
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "33638775_9_792-808",
          "range": "16991-17007",
          "rangeStart": 16991,
          "rangeEnd": 17007,
          "markText": "诸孙相逢万里外，一笑未解千忧积。",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1647389613,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2022-03-16 08:13:33",
          "chapterUid": 148,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=33638775&chapterUid=148&rangeStart=16991&rangeEnd=17007",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ed732f2072014977ed74bf5?chapterUid=148&rangeStart=16991&rangeEnd=17007"
        },
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "33638775_8_4225-4343",
          "range": "15879-15967",
          "rangeStart": 15879,
          "rangeEnd": 15967,
          "markText": "少或百字，多或千言，其指事析理，引物托喻，侈能尽之约，远能见之近，大能使之微，小能使之著，烦能不乱，肆能不流。其雄壮俊伟，若决江河而下也；其辉光明白，若引星辰而上也，其略如是。\n",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1647389293,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2022-03-16 08:08:13",
          "chapterUid": 148,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=33638775&chapterUid=148&rangeStart=15879&rangeEnd=15967",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ed732f2072014977ed74bf5?chapterUid=148&rangeStart=15879&rangeEnd=15967"
        },
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "33638775_8_827-997",
          "range": "12489-12693",
          "rangeStart": 12489,
          "rangeEnd": 12693,
          "markText": "富家不用买良田，书中自有千钟粟。\n安居不用架高堂，书中自有黄金屋。\n娶妻莫恨无良媒，书中自有颜如玉。\n出门莫恨无人随，书中车马多如簇。\n男儿欲遂平生志，五经勤向窗前读。\n",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1647388753,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2022-03-16 07:59:13",
          "chapterUid": 148,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=33638775&chapterUid=148&rangeStart=12489&rangeEnd=12693",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ed732f2072014977ed74bf5?chapterUid=148&rangeStart=12489&rangeEnd=12693"
        },
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "33638775_7_2069-2098",
          "range": "10215-10244",
          "rangeStart": 10215,
          "rangeEnd": 10244,
          "markText": "多财而不施，吾恐他人谋我；然施而使人知之，人将以我为好名。",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1647388366,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2022-03-16 07:52:46",
          "chapterUid": 148,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=33638775&chapterUid=148&rangeStart=10215&rangeEnd=10244",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ed732f2072014977ed74bf5?chapterUid=148&rangeStart=10215&rangeEnd=10244"
        }
      ]
    },
