      "range": "9750-9812",
      "markText": "但是我一直记得李雍在电话中对我说的话：“辉诚老师，您知道吗？您写来第一封信的那天，正好是我父亲的忌日。”世间巧合，竟至于此。",
      "totalCount": 21135,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=33638775&chapterUid=147&rangeStart=9750&rangeEnd=9812",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ed732f2072014977ed74bf5?chapterUid=147&rangeStart=9750&rangeEnd=9812"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "33638775_148_28900-28967",
      "chapterUid": 148,
      "range": "28900-28967",
      "markText": "但是张方平为不埋没苏洵，毅然写信给欧阳修，固然难得，而欧阳修也并不因是张方平介绍，便漠视这个人才，这种风度，求诸后世，几已不易再见了。",
      "totalCount": 10914,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=33638775&chapterUid=148&rangeStart=28900&rangeEnd=28967",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ed732f2072014977ed74bf5?chapterUid=148&rangeStart=28900&rangeEnd=28967"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "33638775_148_8320-8358",
      "chapterUid": 148,
      "range": "8320-8358",
      "markText": "苏轼四十年的政治生活中，被人疏远，永远孤立，受出生地的影响，不能说完全没有。",
      "totalCount": 10183,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=33638775&chapterUid=148&rangeStart=8320&rangeEnd=8358",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ed732f2072014977ed74bf5?chapterUid=148&rangeStart=8320&rangeEnd=8358"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "33638775_148_7846-7938",
      "chapterUid": 148,
      "range": "7846-7938",
      "markText": "苏轼兄弟因农村破产，家业凋零，而不得不出仕，但初至京师，尚在应试阶段，即已思想及早退休还乡，寻求夜雨对床之乐，所谓“未入仕版，已怀归志”。这也是地方性格的表现，与一般人的淡泊不尽相同。",
      "totalCount": 7650,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=33638775&chapterUid=148&rangeStart=7846&rangeEnd=7938",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ed732f2072014977ed74bf5?chapterUid=148&rangeStart=7846&rangeEnd=7938"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "33638775_148_20031-20061",
      "chapterUid": 148,
      "range": "20031-20061",
      "markText": "吾欲使汝为恶，则恶不可为；使汝为善，则我不为恶，而下场如此。",
      "totalCount": 6123,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=33638775&chapterUid=148&rangeStart=20031&rangeEnd=20061",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ed732f2072014977ed74bf5?chapterUid=148&rangeStart=20031&rangeEnd=20061"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "33638775_148_52898-52956",
      "chapterUid": 148,
      "range": "52898-52956",
      "markText": "兄弟俩就在怀远驿做了“风雨对床”的约定，此后四十年间，两人都念念不忘这个旧约，然而由于可悲的人生羁绊，终身不能实现。",
      "totalCount": 6075,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=33638775&chapterUid=148&rangeStart=52898&rangeEnd=52956",
